parameters:
\nc<>The moon is not out and the weather is warm. It's perfect
weather for a walk, isn't it?
\nc<>Ah, are you embarrassed by any chance?

\nc<>Today, you haven't been fighting against any succubi,
right? So why are you doing something like this...

\nc<>Senpai, do you remember the words you said before? The words
no or don't?
\nc<>You seem to have some misunderstanding from the start.
\nc<>I'm not asking you to change clothes.
\nc<>I'm telling you to change clothes, Senpai.

\nc<>(It's not good. Lately, I've been unable to resist this
child's words...)
\nc<>(I should clearly say that it's not allowed here...)
\nc<>Hehe. Look, Senpai. Isn't she so cute?

\nc<>(With dog ears and even a collar... this is just like a
pet...)
\nc<>Alright, it's time for a walk, Senpai.

\nc<>The atmosphere at night school is quite different, isn't it?
Senpai, you think so too, right?

\nc<>(A place I pass by every day.) (Even though I don't have
close friends, there are many people who know my face.)

\nc<>(Doing something like this in a place like this, if someone
were to see, it would really be the end.)
\nc<>(Why is my stomach rumbling like this...)

\nc<>Oh, it looks like there are still people remaining. Being a
graduate student is tough, isn't it?

\nc<>What's wrong? There are people here, you know. Let's go
somewhere else, not here...
\nc<>No, Senpai. We should enjoy our walk slowly.
\nc<>See, it's surprisingly not a big deal--
